    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept and detailed regularly. It honestly looks and drives just like it's brand new; you won't find a single blemish or mechanical issue anywhere. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to someone who will appreciate a ride in such flawless shape, so I've set a really fair price to get things moving. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great new home!",
