    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty! I\u2019m listing my pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in absolute mint condition. It\u2019s been pampered its whole life\u2014super clean, smells like new, and drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 43200.0,
