    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2). This widebody example is powered by the M96/03 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, mated to a 6-speed longitudinal manual transaxle. The viscous multi-plate all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional mechanical grip, complemented by a factory-lowered suspension and red four-piston monobloc calipers. This vehicle is mechanically superlative; the IMS bearing has been proactively upgraded to a ceramic dual-row unit, and the Bore Scoring inspection yielded zero deviations. With zero cowl shake and a pristine undercarriage, this C4S offers a pure, analog driving experience in concours condition. Turnkey and ready for the most discerning collector.",
